  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine chopped basil leaves and sliced red onion.",
    "Add minced garlic cloves and toss well.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together lemon juice and olive oil.",
    "Pour the dressing over the basil mixture and toss to coat.",
    "Add confit tomato and toss gently to combine.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Serve chilled and garnish with additional basil leaves if desired."
  ],
